.Dd $Mdocdate: April 13 2026 $
.Dt ISPI 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ispi
.Nd Intel LPSS SPI controller
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "ispi* at acpi?"
.Cd "ispi* at pci?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver supports the Serial Peripheral Interface (SPI) controller
included in the Intel Low-Power Subsystem (LPSS).
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr acpi 4 ,
.Xr pci 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
device driver first appeared in
.Ox 7.9 .
